guest_message: Hi there! I'm Frank Morrison. I'm looking to order some lunch for me and my grandkids. Can you tell me a bit about your Classic Burger? What's included, and do you have options for the meat temperature?
Hey, thanks for the details! I'll go with the Classic Burger and have it cooked Well Done. Let's add American cheese to that. Would you happen to have a side choice option?
Let's go with the French Fries as the side for the Classic Burger, please. And, could you tell me what options are available for the chicken sandwich as a side?
I'd like to order the Grilled Chicken Sandwich next, please. Can you make that with the Fruit Cup on the side?
Could I add some provolone cheese to the Grilled Chicken Sandwich, please? Thanks!
Great, thanks! I'll pick it up in 20 minutes.
Hi, thanks for the confirmation! Looks like there was a tiny mix-up. I was hoping to add two Fresh Orange Juices, small size, to the order as well. Could you please include those?
Everything looks perfect now! Thanks for the update. Please keep the pickup time for 20 minutes. Looking forward to it!
